h4. Purpose

This tag strips HTML-style markup from the string by matching it and deleting the markup text.

This is desirable when you have some pre-formatted HTML content but wish to have a plain text representation, for example in search results.

*Example*

{code}
Overview: <wcm:htmlToText>${node.content}</wcm:htmlToText>
{code}

h4. Description

There are no attributes.